metadata.name: Moth in a jar
metadata.description:
The picture of the world is blurring. Wherever you look, you're like a moth trapped in a glass jar.
Someone is limiting your viewing angle. Someone is separating your world from reality. Someone covered you with a jar.

Artwork by Sweet Proxy 

Sound Design by Orhydea

15 sec, 25 FPS
2022
1/1
This NFT includes the original animation video, and links to the uncompressed HD videos files
